OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,FRugby League Legend and MND fundraiser
OL,7,FKevin Sinfield said he is 'honoured'
OL,8,Fto be awarded a Knighthood.
OL,10,FIn a glittering career, Sinfield
OL,11,Fcaptained his only club, Leeds Rhinos
OL,12,Fto an incredible 15 major honours in
OL,13,Fan 18-year career.
OL,15,FThe 45-year-old also represented Great
OL,16,FBritain and captained England before
OL,17,Fretiring from playing in 2015, having
OL,18,Fhelped the Rhinos to an unprecedented
OL,19,FTreble.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
