CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,FOff the pitch, he has been applauded
OL,7,Ffor taking on ultra-marathons and
OL,8,Fchallenges to raise money for Motor
OL,9,FNeurone Disease research.
OL,11,FHis extraordinary fundraising efforts
OL,12,Fhave been in memory of his late friend
OL,13,Fand teammate Rob Burrow. Rob was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with the condition in 2019
OL,15,Fand died in June 2024 at the age of 41.
OL,17,FSince the first challenge in 2020,
OL,18,FSinfield and the team have raised more
OL,19,Fthan #11m for the MND community.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
