SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,FSinfield was awarded an MBE in 2014 in
OL,7,Frecognition of his outstanding playing
OL,8,Fcareer and then an OBE in 2021 for his
OL,9,Fwork in raising awareness and funds
OL,10,Ffor those impacted by MND.
OL,12,FLast year, Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fteased the possibility of a knighthood.
OL,15,FNow it has been confirmed that he will
OL,16,Fbe awarded the title in the King's
OL,17,FBirthday Honours.
OL,19,FSinfield expressed his gratitude
OL,20,Ffollowing the announcement.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,F"I am deeply honoured and grateful to
OL,7,Freceive this award on behalf of the
OL,8,FRugby and MND communities.
OL,10,F"Since I first played rugby when I was
OL,11,F7, Rugby League has given me so much.
OL,12,FI am particularly proud to follow in
OL,13,Fthe footsteps of the great Sir Billy
OL,14,FBoston with Rugby League's second ever
OL,15,Fknighthood in over 130 years of the
OL,16,Fsport."
OL,18,FHe continued, "I was privileged to
OL,19,Fplay with some great players for my
OL,20,Fclub and country and made friendships
OL,21,Ffor life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,F"My playing career was everything I
OL,7,Fcould ever have dreamed of as a young
OL,8,Fman but the last seven years have
OL,9,Fgiven me so much inspiration. The MND
OL,10,Fcommunity are the very best of us and
OL,11,Fit has been my privilege to support
OL,12,Fthem and put their battle on the stage
OL,13,Fit needs."
OL,15,FHe thanked his family for their
OL,16,Fsupport and said Rob has been his
OL,17,Fbiggest inspiration for his
OL,18,Ffundraising feats.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,F"I continue to be inspired by the
OL,7,Fcourage that Rob Burrow showed in his
OL,8,Fbattle with the disease and he is
OL,9,Fnever far from my thoughts. We have
OL,10,Fraised so much awareness and funds to
OL,11,Fsupport families and aid research but
OL,12,Fmore needs to be done."
OL,14,FRob Burrow's wife Lindsey Burrow
OL,15,Fwelcomed the news of Sinfield's
OL,16,Frecognition, who called him a
OL,17,F"deserved recipient."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,F"On behalf of the whole Burrow family,
OL,7,FI would like to congratulate Kevin on
OL,8,Fhis knighthood, we are all delighted
OL,9,Ffor him and I can not think of a more
OL,10,Fdeserving recipient. Kevin did so much
OL,11,Ffor Rob but also the whole MND
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"I know he has said he is dedicated to
OL,15,Fsupporting the MND community for
OL,16,Fhowever long it takes to find a cure
OL,17,Fand that means so much to so many
OL,18,Fpeople to have a champion like Kevin
OL,19,Fin their corner.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,F"As Rob used to say, everyone should
OL,7,Fhave a friend like Kevin and so many
OL,8,Fpeople will be pleased to see him get
OL,9,Fthis recognition," she added.
OL,11,FLeeds Rhinos Chief Executive Jamie
OL,12,FJones-Buchanan MBE also weighed in
OL,13,Fwith congratulations for the Rugby
OL,14,Fhero, calling him a "wonderful team
OL,15,Fmate, an inspiring captain but most
OL,16,Fimportantly he remains a great friend."
OL,18,FHe added, "I am so proud today for him
OL,19,Fthat he has been recognised by the
OL,20,Fnation in this way."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
