PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781385839
OL,3,CKevin Sinfield 'honoured' to receive
OL,4,CKnighthood for MND fundraising
OL,6,FIn September, Sinfield will begin his
OL,7,Fseventh and final challenge which will
OL,8,Fsee him run an ultra marathon every
OL,9,Fday for seven days in September.
OL,11,FThe route will include all 12 Betfred
OL,12,FSuper League grounds on his way from
OL,13,FHull KR's Craven Park to Old Trafford
OL,14,Fin Manchester. The final endurance
OL,15,Ftest will see him arrive onto the
OL,16,Fpitch in time for the Super League
OL,17,FGrand Final on Saturday 3 October.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
